d')\t\t\tAS ConsumptionMethod , \r\nJSON_VALUE(AuditData, '$.ArtifactKind') \t\t\t\tAS ArtifactKind,\r\nJSON_VALUE(AuditData, '$.RefreshEnforcementPolicy') \tAS RefreshEnforcementPolicy,\r\nGetdate() \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAS LastUpdatedTS\r\n\r\n\tfrom ODS.POWERBI_AUDIT_LOGS",
